# Workflow
- Start each major task by updating docs/architecture.md or a service-specific doc if the task changes architecture.
- Before editing many files, summarize the intended change in chat.
- Run focused tests first, then the broader service test suite.
- Keep route handlers thin.
- Keep MCP tools thin.
- Prefer composition over inheritance.
- Add TODO markers only when accompanied by a doc entry or issue reference.